134
00:06:25,208 --> 00:06:26,663
avec un balle dans sa bouche.

135
00:06:26,768 --> 00:06:28,213
Inspire Ricky Martin...

136
00:06:28,316 --> 00:06:29,931
expire Colin Farrell.

137
00:06:30,038 --> 00:06:32,501
